comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-05T23:06:03.204Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm context --limit 10; pm search 'validate lifecycle stale blocker configurable patterns' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Net-new because existing lifecycle guardrails ship static heuristics but no settings-backed pattern policy surface."
  "2026-04-25T20:04:47.301Z",codex-agent,"2026-04-25 validate sweep still reports lifecycle advisories: active_closure_like_metadata for pm-a4z3/pm-cvwi/pm-kglq/pm-r15d and active_terminal_parent for pm-0nxf, pm-a4z3, pm-cvwi, pm-i4ef, pm-p0ij, pm-umhv, pm-urxb. This follow-up remains open as policy/lineage normalization work."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-05T23:06:03.204Z",codex-agent,Implement deterministic pattern-source reporting (default vs settings override) and preserve warning token stability by default.
